## Overview

**InceptaX** is a production-grade hackathon platform built for developers who want to prove their skills. Users tackle real-world coding challenges, submit GitHub repositories, and receive detailed AI-generated feedback. An entirely separate admin portal controls challenge creation, AI evaluation triggers, submission review, and result publishing.

The platform enforces a **manual review pipeline** тАФ AI never auto-publishes scores. Every result goes through admin approval before users see it, ensuring quality and fairness.

---

## Features

### User Side
- **Firebase Authentication** тАФ Google, GitHub, or Email sign-in
- **OTP Email Verification** тАФ 6-digit code sent via Nodemailer on new sign-ups
- **Browse Challenges** тАФ Filter by difficulty (Easy / Medium / Hard) and Free vs Premium
- **Project Submission** тАФ Submit a GitHub repo URL, live demo link, and description
- **Team Collaboration** тАФ Invite partners by username (Premium plans only)
- **Real-time Team Chat** тАФ Socket.io text chat within a shared submission (Premium only)
- **Per-Project Leaderboard** тАФ See your rank within every individual challenge
- **Global Leaderboard** тАФ Ranked by best project score across all challenges
- **Portfolio Profile** тАФ Unique public URL per user: `/u/:username`
- **Shareable Profile Link** тАФ One-click copy of your public profile URL
- **Subscription Plans** тАФ Free / 10-Day Sprint (тВ╣99) / Monthly Pro (тВ╣199)

### Admin Portal (Completely Separate)
- **Isolated at `/admin-portal`** тАФ Different login, different JWT, no Firebase
- **Challenge Management** тАФ Create, edit, delete challenges with premium gating
- **Manual AI Trigger** тАФ Admin presses a button to run OpenAI evaluation on any submission
- **Submission Review** тАФ Set admin score, add internal notes, approve or reject
- **Publish & Rank** тАФ Publishing a submission auto-recomputes all ranks for that challenge
- **User Management** тАФ View all users, manually grant or revoke plans
- **Email Blast** тАФ Send HTML emails to all users or filter by plan (Free / Sprint / Pro)
- **Email Logs** тАФ Full history of every email sent through the platform
- **Stats Dashboard** тАФ Live counts of users, challenges, published results, pending reviews

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS, React Router v6 |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB, Mongoose |
| Auth (Users) | Firebase Authentication (Google, GitHub, Email+Password) |
| Auth (Admin) | Custom JWT (bcrypt-hashed passwords, separate secret) |
| AI Evaluation | OpenAI GPT-3.5 Turbo |
| GitHub Data | GitHub REST API v3 (README + file tree fetch) |
| Real-time Chat | Socket.io |
| Email | Nodemailer (SMTP / Gmail App Password) |
| OTP Verification | Custom 6-digit code + MongoDB TTL index |

