### Challenges

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/assignments` | Public | List challenges (filter: difficulty, search, premium) |
| `GET` | `/api/assignments/:id` | Public | Get single challenge detail |

### Submissions

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/api/submissions` | Firebase | Submit a project |
| `GET` | `/api/submissions/mine` | Firebase | Get own submissions |
| `GET` | `/api/submissions/:id` | Firebase | Get single submission (published or own) |
| `GET` | `/api/submissions/assignment/:id` | Public | Published submissions for a challenge |
| `GET` | `/api/submissions/user/:username` | Public | Published portfolio for a user |

### Leaderboard

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/leaderboard` | Public | Global rankings |
| `GET` | `/api/leaderboard/assignment/:id` | Public | Per-challenge rankings |

### Plans

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/plans` | Public | Pricing plan info |
| `POST` | `/api/plans/upgrade` | Firebase | Activate a paid plan |

### OTP

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/api/otp/send` | Public | Send 6-digit verification code |
| `POST` | `/api/otp/verify` | Public | Verify submitted code |

### Team Chat

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/chat/:submissionId` | Firebase + Premium | Get message history |
| `POST` | `/api/chat/:submissionId` | Firebase + Premium | Send a message |

